node.text: Take Action for Our Brighter Future 🏆💖 The 36th Annual Sanrio Character Ranking Contest is here! Tap the link in bio to vote for your favorite characters✨  The winner will be announced later this summer and included in a special capsule collection. Don't forget to share on social by tagging #SanrioCharacterRanking and @sanrio for a chance to be featured!⁠

node.text: From @hellokitty, My Melody, to Keroppi, get ready to discover new residents, styles and items inspired by adorable Sanrio friends! 🍃💞 The #AnimalCrossing Sanrio Collaboration Pack comes to the US on 3/26, exclusively at @target!

node.text: SUPER SWEET NEWS!✨ Hello Kitty and Friends Supercute Adventures is coming back for another season full of fun, new adventures! 🌈☁️ Season 3 premieres on August 25th only on the #HelloKittyandFriends YouTube channel. Link in bio to subscribe! ⁠

node.text: If there’s one character that likes to be as stylish as Hello Kitty, it’s our dapper Friend of the Month! 🐧💙Follow along as we show you how to draw Hello Kitty’s red bow and her friend, #Tuxedosam on the #HelloKittyandFriends YouTube channel. Link in bio ✨
